data.description: Gorgeous and fully updated 4 bedroom/2 bathroom pool home on 1/3 acre in Cypress Creek! Cypress Creek is the hidden gem of Boynton Beach with a 24 hr guard gate and an HOA of only $117/month! RVs and boats allowed! This beautiful home is spacious and open. Updated kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Two spacious living rooms and enormous fenced-in backyard. Indoor laundry room with front loader washer/dryer and a laundry sink. Brand new hot water heater. The fourth bedroom is off of the master and is ideal for an office or nursery. Lots of windows, corner lot and hurricane shutters. AC is 2020. You don't want to miss your chance to live in this perfect home in Cypress Creek!
